Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you do not receive your approval notice by July 31, 2021, please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Case Was Received
body: On May 21, 2021, we received your Form I-765, Application for Employment Authorization, Receipt Number YSC2190170988, and sent you the receipt notice that describes how we will process your case. Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you have any questions, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Card Is Being Returned to USCIS by Post Office
body: On July 19, 2021, the Post Office reported that they are returning your new card for Receipt Number YSC2190170989, to us. We mailed your card to the address you gave us, but the Post Office could not deliver it. The tracking number assigned is 9205590153708409716470. You can use your tracking number at www.USPS.com in the Quick Tools Tracking section. Please go to www.uscis.gov/e-request to request that we resend the card to you. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
